DESCRIPTION:Join the Outdoor Adventure programs for some informal gatherings of bike-minded people at GVSU. We'll share our passion for all things bicycle related\, enjoy some food\, & keep the stoke high as we wait for more ideal temps for outdoor riding. All riders are welcome\, from serious to curious in any style.\nAll meetings will run from 4p-5\:30p. The activities and locations will vary based on seasons and general interest but we've put together a few gatherings to get things started.\nSchedule\n Sunday\, February 22 \n \n Kirkhof 2266. - General meet & greet with bike related activities + Jets pizza\n \n \n Sunday\, March 29\n \n Rec Center Instructional Fitness Studio - brief indoor \"group ride\" w/ some rad bike documentary on the big screen.\n \n \n Sunday\, April 19 (Canceled)\n \n Ravines Center - grab your bike & join us for informal bike challenges in the parking-lot. Tacos likely.\n \n \nRSVP requested for food planning purposes & for announcing any last-minute changes.\n \n RSVP for this event\n \nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-536219.htm
SUMMARY:Social Spokes Sundays - Canceled
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
