DESCRIPTION:Feeling unsure about life after graduation? Your summer plans? You're not alone.\nStop by 200 STU from 1-3pm on Tuesday April 21st to connect with GVSU's CARE Team and Career Center staff\, explore helpful resources\, and leave with 'next steps' for your future! Attendees will be able to snack on FREE ice cream and popcorn while discussing meaningful ways to plan for the future.\nQuestions? Reach out to Rowan Hawthorne at s_armourow@gvsu.edu.\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-525948.htm
SUMMARY:CARE About Your Next Steps
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
