DTEND:20260421T160000
DESCRIPTION:During Drop-In hours our SASC Success Coaches will be hanging out in the Knowledge Market at the Mary Idema Pew Library ready to chat! You can make a study plan\, learn about different study strategies\, and ask about study tips or success coaching. Come check out our resources and worksheets! These drop-in hours will be hosted on Tuesday\, April 21 from 2\:30-4 (Mary Idema Pew Library)\, Wednesday\, April 22 from 11-12\:30 (Kirkhof) and Thursday\, April 23 from 11-12\:30 (Kirkhof). \nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-535393.htm
SUMMARY:Final Exam Drop In Hours
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
