DTSTART:20260421T150000
DTEND:20260421T170000
DESCRIPTION:INT 100 & 201 Approved!\nAll are welcome to join us for a meaningful\, hands-on gathering in recognition of Sexual Assault Awareness Month.\nSexual violence often exists in silence and in the shadows. During this interactive event\, we will come together to shed light\, break silence\, and stand in solidarity with survivors. Learn more about campus resources and what you can do to prevent sexual assault. Create a candle for yourself\, for someone you love\, or as a tribute to sexual assault survivors. \nRefreshments and all materials will be provided. \n \nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-521066.htm
SUMMARY:Craftivism\: Candle-Making for Sexual Assault Awareness Month (INT 100/201 approved)
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
