DESCRIPTION:FBI Collegiate Academy at GVSU!\nJoin us for a full day of engaging FBI-led seminars\, live demonstrations\, and interactive Q&A sessions. This is a unique opportunity to learn about careers in criminal justice\, cybersecurity\, and many other fields directly from FBI professionals. Whether you're a CJ major or exploring other career paths\, this event has something for everyone.\n Location\: PEW Campus - Loosemore Auditorium\n Date\: April 22nd\, 2026\n Light breakfast and lunch will be provided\n Students who attend the full day will receive a Certificate of Completion\n Registration is required for all attendees\nThis event is open to ALL GVSU students\, so don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to connect\, learn\, and explore future career paths.\nCheck out the flyer above for more details and registration information!\nhttps\://www.gvsu.edu/cj/cms-form-edit.htm?formId=6FB905F1-DACF-F83F-37D3345BC7F7914D\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-531082.htm
SUMMARY:FBI Collegiate Academy
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
