DESCRIPTION:Join the Center for Health & Well-being throughout April for Wellness Wednesday tabling events in recognition of Sexual Assault Awareness Month. Each week focuses on practical skills\, empowerment\, and ways we can create a safer\, more respectful campus community. Stop by\, learn something new\, and grab free resources and giveaways.\nHealthy relationships begin with understanding and honoring boundaries. Stop by to reflect on body autonomy\, practice boundary-setting skills\, and explore how empowerment connects to overall wellness.\nClick here for additional information\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-518180.htm
SUMMARY:Wednesday Wellness - SAAM - My Body\, My Boundaries
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
