DESCRIPTION:Since its founding\, the College of Computing at GVSU has been dedicated to building strong partnerships with industry and the community. We pride ourselves on always questioning the status quo and innovating to better serve our students. Through initiatives to modernize our curriculum and engage in cutting-edge research\, we are committed to finding new ways to lead in the field of computing. \nThis years Computing + X Innovation Day celebrates how computing transforms every field it touches - the arts\, business\, criminal justice\, education\, health\, humanities\, nursing\, the sciences\, and beyond. From AI-driven discovery to data-powered decision-making\, we are exploring how computing fuels innovation across disciplines.\nregister HERE\nLEARN MORE ABOUT INNOVATION DAY\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-522246.htm
SUMMARY:Innovation Day\: Computing + X
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
