DESCRIPTION:ARE YOU JUGGLING MULTIPLE ROLES? \nYou are not alone.\n1 in 5 undergraduate students are raising children. \nThis virtual parent support meet-up is for anyone juggling the roles of parent and college student. This is a informal group\: if you need to join late\, leave early\, bring your kids\, or wear your jammies\, WE GET IT. No judgement here. Learn and share resources and hacks\, share your experiences- good and bad\, and help advocate for the needs of parenting Lakers like you. \nPlease register to receive the Zoom link\: https\://www.gvsu.edu/cwge/cms-form-edit.htm?formId=8E484C37-D760-62F8-4347E12372B2D66A\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-534244.htm
SUMMARY:Virtual Parent Support Meet Up
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
