DESCRIPTION:Lakerpalooza 2026\nOne last hurrah before summer! Come celebrate the end of the school year with your fellow Lakers at Lakerpalooza on Friday\, April 24 from 5-9 p.m. on the Kirkhof Lawn.\nEnjoy an evening packed with fun and celebration\, featuring\:\n Inflatables\n Food trucks\n Games & activities\n Caricature artists\n &hellip\;and so much more!\nBring your friends\, soak up the spring vibes\, and send off the year with memories you'll never forget!\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-467706.htm
