DESCRIPTION:Were so excited to invite all students to our upcoming dance showcasean energetic\, feel-good event you wont want to miss! Come out and support your peers as they take the stage and bring a variety of dance styles to life through creativity\, passion\, and hard work. Whether you love dance or just want something fun to do\, this is a great chance to relax\, enjoy the music\, and be part of an uplifting atmosphere.\nThis showcase is more than just a performanceits a celebration of self-expression\, confidence\, and community. Our organization is dedicated to creating a welcoming space where students can connect\, grow\, and share their talents\, and this event truly reflects that mission. Bring your friends\, come ready to cheer\, and enjoy a night full of excitement and unforgettable performances!Competencies\:Fun and Enjoyment\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-533005.htm
