DESCRIPTION:Are you interested in teaching English abroad? Are you curious about studying for a Master's degree abroad? The Fulbright program might be for you! Join me to learn more!\nFor more Information about Fulbright possibilities and application procedures\n1) Explore the Fulbright U.S. Student website.\n2) Search Types of Awards and take a look at which countries Fulbright may take you.\n3) Explore Fulbright Tutorials to learn more about grant types and eligibility.\n4) Visit the Getting Started page to learn more about next steps.\nClick here for additional information\nRSVP for this event\nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-535941.htm
SUMMARY:Fulbright US Student Program - Virtual Information Session
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
