DESCRIPTION:Groundswell will host its annual Student Project Showcase for educators\, community members\, students\, and families. Groundswell is proud to celebrate the work of student stewards in an interactive event with participating K12 schools. Students will host tables at an exhibit fair\, offering insight for attendees about their community stewardship activities. Please join us to help recognize student-led efforts to protect the Grand River and Great Lakes.\nThis event is free and open to the public. \nAdditional information can be found on our Student Project Showcase Webpage\n \n Click here for additional information\n \nhttps\://gvsu.edu/events/event-528750.htm
SUMMARY:Groundswell Student Project Showcase 2026
PRIORITY:3
END:VEVENT
